title: PM Modi’s guru Swami Dayanand Giri no more
text:
Other Articles Letters to the editor Search for MH370 to revisit more than 30 sites earlier ruled out High Cout disblieves Hardik Patel's kidnap story, warns of contempt action Prime Minister Narendra Modi ’s guru Swami Dayanand Giri breathed his last here this evening.
As per reports, he passed away at his ashram here at around 10: 20 pm. He had been critical for the last three days. His last rites will take place on Friday.
Prime Minister Modi had met Swami Dayanand Giri during his visit to Uttarakhand on September 11.
 24, 2015 3:00 pm
